Stadium Ticket RESTful API for POSIX Operating Systems

1.  To install dependencies (may require sudo):

    scripts/install-dependencies.sh

2.  To initialize the database schema:

    scripts/run.sh python3 -m app init-db

3.  To reset the database to a known state (with test data):

    scripts/run.sh python3 -m app reload-db

4.  To run the unit tests using pytest:

    scripts/run.sh pytest

5.  To run the app:

    scripts/run.sh flask run

6.  To test the app:

    scripts/app-test.sh

7.  To stress test the app:

    scripts/load-test.sh

8.  To build and run a Docker container:

    scripts/run.sh docker-compose up --build
